                  </persName> was <hi rend="italic">again</hi> indicted<rs id="t18490507-1082-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18490507-1082-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18490507-1082-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing 3lbs. weight of tea, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18490507-name-160" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18490507-name-160" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
